data.description: WOW!! $20,000 reduction in List Price!! Sharp 2 bed 2 bath SITE BUILT home in The Villages of Delmar. New roof, HVAC and Hot water tank! Landscaping and Kitchen appliances have been updated. Beautifully decorated and freshly painted with Caribbean colors!  Inside laundry room with NEW washer/dryer with ample cabinets for storage! No bond! No carpet! Laminate and Tile flooring throughout! Gorgeous private backyard with beautiful gardens. Large Florida room.  Cozy porch off living room. Golfcart Garage. FREE HOME WATCH for one year if you are a SNOWBIRD! FREE LAWN CARE for one year!! A $!,000 value!! Just a short walk to Spanish Springs Square and minutes to Lake Sumter Square. Hospital minutes away. This is a MUST SEE at this price reduction!
